en_966908_0	The Officer-in -Charge of the Wellampitiya Police  and is wife have been arrested  for alleged Heroin possession.
en_966908_1	According to the Police Media Spokesperson, SSP Ajith Rohana, the OIC of the Wellampitiya Police was arrested on Tuesday evening by the Colombo Crimes Division.
en_966908_2	Following interrogation, the wife of the OIC was also arrested on Wednesday.
